{
  "chapter": 15,
  "chapter_summary": "本章以月神与小星的深夜对话为核心，揭示了正月十五之约的深层矛盾。月神作为薛家后人，必须向李家挑战以维护家族荣誉，而对手李曼青作为小李探花的后代同样不能败。更令人揪心的是，月神与李家后人李坏相爱并已育有一子，但两人却不得不在正月十五一决生死。月神拒绝告诉李坏孩子的存在，认为这是心甘情愿的选择。最终面对小星的追问，月神坦言不知李坏能否忍心杀她，她也不知自己能否忍心杀李坏，道出了命运的无奈与悲剧色彩。章尾以哲理性的旁白收束，点明生死只是一刹那，情感却是永恒的主题。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xing",
      "speaker_name": "小星",
      "listener": "char_yue_shen",
      "text": "小姐，正月十五那天，我一定也要陪你过去。因为我要看看那个李曼青究竟是个什么样的人，当年为什么要把老爹逼得那么惨。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xing",
      "speaker_name": "小星",
      "listener": "char_yue_shen",
      "text": "我娘告诉我这件事的时候，我就一直在盼望着有一天能亲眼看到这个李曼青死在小姐你的刀下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_shen",
      "speaker_name": "月神",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xing",
      "text": "李曼青不会死在我刀下的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_shen",
      "speaker_name": "月神",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xing",
      "text": "因为正月十五那天，他根本不会应战。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xing",
      "speaker_name": "小星",
      "listener": "char_yue_shen",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xing",
      "speaker_name": "小星",
      "listener": "char_yue_shen",
      "text": "难道李曼青是个贪生怕死的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_shen",
      "speaker_name": "月神",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xing",
      "text": "他不怕死，可是他怕败。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_shen",
      "speaker_name": "月神",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xing",
      "text": "他是小李探花的后代，他不能败。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xing",
      "speaker_name": "小星",
      "listener": "char_yue_shen",
      "text": "小姐，李坏李少爷难道真的是他们李家的后代？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_shen",
      "speaker_name": "月神",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xing",
      "text": "恩。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xing",
      "speaker_name": "小星",
      "listener": "char_yue_shen",
      "text": "那么他一定不知道向李家挑战的人就是你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_shen",
      "speaker_name": "月神",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xing",
      "text": "他知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_shen",
      "speaker_name": "月神",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xing",
      "text": "他是个绝顶聪明的人，现在他一定已经知道了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xing",
      "speaker_name": "小星",
      "listener": "char_yue_shen",
      "text": "如果他真的知道，正月十五那一天他的对手就是你，他就应该走得远远的。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xing",
      "speaker_name": "小星",
      "listener": "char_yue_shen",
      "text": "他怎么能忍心对你出手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_shen",
      "speaker_name": "月神",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xing",
      "text": "因为他别无选择的余地。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xing",
      "speaker_name": "小星",
      "listener": "char_yue_shen",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_shen",
      "speaker_name": "月神",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xing",
      "text": "因为他不管怎么样，他都是李家的子孙。他绝不能让李家的尊荣毁在他的手里。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_shen",
      "speaker_name": "月神",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xing",
      "text": "就正如我虽然明知我的对手一定会是他，我也不能让薛家的尊荣毁在我的手里。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_shen",
      "speaker_name": "月神",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xing",
      "text": "天下本来就有很多无可奈何的事，在某一种情况中，一个人明明知道自己做的事不对，也不能不做下去。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xing",
      "speaker_name": "小星",
      "listener": "char_yue_shen",
      "text": "小姐，你为什么不告诉他，你已经替他生了个孩子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_shen",
      "speaker_name": "月神",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xing",
      "text": "我为什么要告诉他？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_shen",
      "speaker_name": "月神",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xing",
      "text": "我替他生这个孩子，并不是为了要替他们李家留一个后代，我替他生的这个孩子，虽然是他们李家的后代，也同样是我们薛家的后代。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_shen",
      "speaker_name": "月神",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xing",
      "text": "这是我心甘情愿的事，我为什么要告诉他？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xing",
      "speaker_name": "小星",
      "listener": "char_yue_shen",
      "text": "可是，如果你告诉了他，他也许就不会对你出手了。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_shen",
      "speaker_name": "月神",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xing",
      "text": "如果我告诉了他，他不忍杀我，我还是一定会杀了他，因为我也非胜不可，而胜就是生，败就是死。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xing",
      "speaker_name": "小星",
      "listener": "char_yue_shen",
      "text": "小姐，现在我只想问你一句话。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_shen",
      "speaker_name": "月神",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xing",
      "text": "你问。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_shen",
      "speaker_name": "月神",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xing",
      "text": "什么话你都可以问。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xing",
      "speaker_name": "小星",
      "listener": "char_yue_shen",
      "text": "到了那一天，到了那争生死，争胜负，争存亡的那一刹那间，他会不会忍心下手杀你？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_shen",
      "speaker_name": "月神",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xing",
      "text": "我不知道。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xing",
      "speaker_name": "小星",
      "listener": "char_yue_shen",
      "text": "那么，到了那一刻，你是不是能忍心杀得了他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_shen",
      "speaker_name": "月神",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xing",
      "text": "我也不知道。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    }
  ],
